<i>noun</i>: 사죄 [사ː죄/사ː줴], 사과 [사ː과] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사죄 [사ː죄/사ː줴]</dt><br>
<dd>apology</dd><br>
<dd>지은 죄나 잘못에 대해 용서를 구함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of seeking forgiveness for one's wrongdoing or fault.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사과 [사ː과]</dt><br>
<dd>apology</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 잘못을 인정하며 용서해 달라고 빎.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of admitting one's own mistakes and begging for forgiveness.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>